<div id=content>
    <h1>Welcome all!</h1>
    <p>
        Hello Everybody and welcome to my homepage. Explore throught the jungle of
        bodged together pages (Yay for bodging together!), and feel free to leave a
        comment - once I've made a way for you to put in comments that is.
    </p>
    <p>
        Check out my projects in the projects tab!
    </p>
    <p>
        Enjoy and have fun!
    </p>
    <div id="projects">
        <% @projects.each do |p| %>
            <div class="project blob">
                <%= link_to image_tag(p.image_url, width: "250", class: "project-image"), p.live_url %>
                <a href="<%= p.live_url %>"><h3><%= p.name %></h3></a>
                <a href="<%= p.repo_url %>"><p>See the code</p></a>
                <p>Built on: <% p.tech.each do |t| %>
                    <%= image_tag(@techs.find_by(name: t).image_url, height: "24") %>
                <% end %></p>
                <p><%= p.description %></p>
            </div>
        <% end %>
    </div>
</div>